      "content": "thanks, that makes me feel better. i'll try the ibuprofen now. what about the oxy though? i have some leftover from a dental surgery last year. would it be okay to take that with the ibuprofen if the pain is still really sharp after an hour? i just really need to pass out so i don't have to deal with this until morning.",
